{"tid":1521840,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急］街坊快d落街接放學！","createTime":"2019-08-31T11:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T12:11:12.000Z","uid":89538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"76d8d6d9ae36ec3e00275e184b6711a7ed3c32d3","tid":1521840,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:07:49.000Z","msg":"帶衫比小朋友換<br />\n帶遮以防落雨有狗<br />\n食物水爽身粉梳打粉 都要！！！"},{"pid":"508a0e1de1662044caa732c788a0456287f51ec6","tid":1521840,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"地區的兒子需要<span style=\"color: red;\">接送 睇水</span><br />\n<br />\n要拖鞋換 小心螢光鞋底路<br />\n<br />\nGASTBY 冰紙巾好似抹到"},{"pid":"6cc64e0801bc35b5ebeed5521013724ce0b5baa0","tid":1521840,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=7adeada0\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=13def80c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=e4de15c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"4e0bde079a72c40593aed4c48af6d0b0c41e65bf","tid":1521840,"uid":241458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"今晚唔只係轉場，係屋企要人"},{"pid":"3a8d132afcfbb844383163be0a47e4c7cdfc2ee7","tid":1521840,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n1. hot sodium carbonate solution<br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾<br />\n<br />\n3.化妝水/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢<br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal"},{"pid":"a4afcc94692ce2142b223bb3d07dc2477bbd438a","tid":1521840,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:15:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b70fbec5c2c586ae9d225ac82daccba3363fd2d","tid":1521840,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:08:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e7e076678ac5695df483d3d9013fdf4f2986450a","tid":1521840,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直接用梘</span></span></strong><br />\n有手足試過work呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sKMOCQq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsKMOCQq.jpg&h=02d62fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外國當年purple Rain Protest水炮車顏料示威者<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">都係用番梘</span></span></strong>洗=洗得甩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yz5jKvV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYz5jKvV.jpg&h=1413a946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麻煩大家幫手spread開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPush"},{"pid":"6bad4bffe3c7fdeb0f2e53d02fd7e86fc5fc9864","tid":1521840,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:11:12.000Z","msg":"呼籲各區街坊，帶齊以下物品<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 長袖衫+褲<br />\n2. 鞋+襪<br />\n3. 帽<br />\n4. 袋<br />\n5. 酒精濕紙巾/落妝水<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">往各區地鐵及巴士站接仔女放學</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>請盡一分力，守護同路人，守護香港未來</strong></span>"}]}